dct_alternative_sm: Qvomodo Franciscvs Draco civitatem S. Dominico in insula Hispaniola
dct_description_sm: Index: Explicatio numerorum in tabula consignatorum.
Depicts Drake's attack on Santo Domingo.
Shows buildings, English fleet, sunken ships and ships on fire, artillery, soldiers, vegetation, alligator.
From de Bry's Grand voyages (Part XIII), 1599.
